

<div class="container-fluid ">
    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-md-3 ">
            <div class="table-left shadow">
                <h4 class="text-center">Single Product Data  </h4>
                <a href="/create" class="buttun-design"> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-left"></i> Back Create Product</a>
                <a href="/" class="buttun-design"> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-left"></i> Back Product Dashbord</a>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 my-2">
               
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                
                <div class="col-md-9">
                    <div class="card shadow">
                        <div class="card-header text-center">
                            <h2><%= product.name %></h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="product-image">
                                <img src="/product/<%= product.photo %>" class="w-100 mb-2" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-table">
                                <table class="table table-striped table-dark">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <th>SI No</th>
                                            <th>Specification</th>
                                            <th>Discription</th> 
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    
                                    <tbody>

                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <td>1</td>
                                            <td>Name</td>
                                            <td><%= product.name %></td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <td>2</td>
                                            <td>Colors</td>
                                            <td><%= product.colors %></td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <td>3</td>
                                            <td>Photo</td>
                                            <td>
                                          
                                                    <img style="height: 60px;
                                                     width: 60px;
                                                     object-fit: cover;
                                                     border-radius: 50%;
                                                     border: 2px solid white;"
                                                     src="/product/<%= product.photo  %>"
                                                     alt="product image">
                                               
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <td>3</td>
                                            <td>Brand</td>
                                            <td><%= product.brand %></td>
                                        </tr>


                                        <tr class="align-middle">
                                            <td>4</td>
                                            <td>Regular Price</td>
                                            <td><%= product.regularPrice %> Taka</td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle" >
                                            <td>5</td>
                                            <td>Sale Price</td>
                                            <td><%= product.salePrice %> Taka</td>
                                        </tr>

                                        
                                        <tr class="align-middle" >
                                            <td>6</td>
                                            <td>Size</td>
                                            <td><%= product.size %> Inch</td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle" >
                                            <td>6</td>
                                            <td>Weight</td>
                                            <td><%= product.weight %> kgs</td>
                                        </tr>

                                        <tr class="align-middle" >
                                            <td>7</td>
                                            <td>Stock </td>
                                            <td><%= product.stock %> pcs</td>
                                        </tr>


                                    </tbody>

                                </table>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer " style="background-color: #2c3e50; color: white;">
                            <h3>Product Discription</h3>
                            <p style="font-size: 14px;  color: white;">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Perferendis et tempore aspernatur, voluptatibus sapiente laudantium deleniti amet vero fugit cupiditate dicta quibusdam totam nobis blanditiis nam! Quidem, animi? Consectetur veritatis expedita nemo itaque, facilis ab dolores aliquid et totam doloremque placeat dolore labore voluptate, nulla ipsam iure minus laudantium? Voluptatem.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
              </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>





